mpics team will bring you recaps, coverage and color - including on the ground in Paris - online and on air over the next few weeks.\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"score\": 0.9999999563510765, \"rank\": 2.2084546219494602e-08, \"text\": \"NPR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\"}, {\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999897838734, \"rank\": 1.021609230620656e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian Mann  Lee Kiefer, of Team USA, reacts as she competes with Canada's Yunjia Zhang in the women's team foil semifinal match Thursday at the Grand Palais in Paris.Rebecca Blackwell/APhide caption  NPR is in Paris for the 2024 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Mann\", \"score\": 0.9999993508465483, \"rank\": 6.491281511530512e-07, \"text\": \"Brian Mann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Mann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Mann\"}, {\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lee Kiefer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\"}, {\"begin\": 512, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.8742785248585734, \"rank\": 0.0834636759628407, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8903118184664054, \"rank\": 0.12305347925562182, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wiley-Blackwell\", \"score\": 0.9999777449152516, \"rank\": 2.1792629799169387e-05, \"text\": \"Blackwell\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wiley-Blackwell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wiley-Blackwell\"}, {\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"score\": 0.9999999563510765, \"rank\": 2.2084546219494602e-08, \"text\": \"NPR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\"}, {\"begin\": 695, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999897838734, \"rank\": 1.021609230620656e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more of our coverage from the Games, head toour latest updates.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS - Under the soaring glass dome of Paris's Grand Palais, American fencer Lee Kiefer danced close, clashing foils with her Canadian opponent Eleanor Harvey in a semifinal match.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999897838734, \"rank\": 1.021609230620656e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 862, \"end\": 870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999978055390327, \"rank\": 1.9621444837946403e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lee Kiefer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\"}, {\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9965781302077926, \"rank\": 0.003431155160162739, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eleanor_Harvey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eleanor Harvey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eleanor_Harvey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eleanor_Harvey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The foil is a slender, wand-like sword, wielded with lightning speed.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kiefer scored touch after touch, celebrating each time with a shout, a fist pump or a jubilant leap into the air.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kiefer's win helped propel the U.S. women into the team finals, where they faced Italy, the top-seeded team.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9119429107621102, \"rank\": 0.09278360428382018, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thursday evening the U.S. prevailed again in an upset with 45 touches to Italy's 39 to take gold.\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Americans have grown a lot,\\\" said Italy's Alice Volpi after the match.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.1311195836233602e-13, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 1416, \"end\": 1421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9119429107621102, \"rank\": 0.09278360428382018, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1430, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Volpi\", \"score\": 0.9999999995370672, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Volpi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Volpi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Volpi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We knew that it would be difficult.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were better than us today.\\\"\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This marked the first-ever team gold medal for the U.S. women - and a third gold medal for Kiefer.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kiefer wonindividual gold on Sundayin Paris adding to the one she scored three years ago in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1716, \"end\": 1721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9649947989847221, \"rank\": 0.036274930731921284, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Huang Qianqian, left, competes with United States' Lauren Scruggs in the women's team foil quarterfinal on Thursday at the 2024 Paris Olympics.Rebecca Blackwell/APhide caption  \\\"No matter how much I tried to prepare, there is still so much pressure I put on myself to just fence well and stay present,\\\" Kiefer said after winning her individual final.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1724, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.989484480218315, \"rank\": 0.010171134941616476, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.99888677228769, \"rank\": 0.0006594462450390477, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Scruggs\", \"score\": 0.9999934662759814, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lauren Scruggs\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Scruggs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Scruggs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Each day was a rollercoaster, but here we are at the top.\\\"\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kiefer began fencing at the age of five.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2185, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's now a medical student at the University of Kentucky College of Medicine and is married to fellow Team USA fencer Gerek Meinhardt.\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2289, \"end\": 2297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.8742785248585734, \"rank\": 0.0834636759628407, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerek_Meinhardt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gerek Meinhardt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerek_Meinhardt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerek_Meinhardt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's so special to have my family (here),\\\" Kiefer said after her Sunday victory.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I tried to spot them in the crowd.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it makes it so much fuller.\\\"\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Grand Palais is a breathtaking venue for the fencing competitions and provided the perfect backdrop for the  historic U.S. victory.\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading...\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sponsor Message  Become an NPR sponsor\", \"from\": 2624, \